data.description: Welcome to this charming ranch nestled on a spacious 1.7-acre lot with endless potential. This inviting property offers three bedrooms and two bathrooms spread across a comfortable living space. As you approach, you'll appreciate its tranquil setting, set back from the road, offering privacy and serenity.  Upon entering, you'll find a cozy interior with cathedral ceilings in the kitchen and living room and ample natural light flooding through the windows, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The freshly painted walls and new carpet provide a pristine and welcoming feel. The detached two-car garage provides convenient parking and storage space.  Outside, the expansive lot offers a blank canvas for your imagination to run wild. Whether you dream of creating a lush garden oasis, installing a pool, or building a custom outdoor entertaining area, the possibilities are endless.  With your creativity, this home has the potential to be transformed into your own personal sanctuary. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your dream home!  All appliances "As is", Detached garage "As is"
